show.title: Commander Shourya
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/VCdsFX
show.description: Hawaldar Shourya is docile, obedient and powerless in front of his superiors and local goons. In a village scarred by corrupt officials and violent criminals, school teacher Indira becomes Shourya's catalyst as she awakens the hidden Commander inside the Hawaldar. Putting behind his traumatic past, Shourya transforms into the force that saves the lives of countless children from the evils of Raka and his axis of evil.
